{
  "id": "69c723f47ecd1447baa531e5",
  "title": "非文芸的サイコソフィア",
  "created": 1774658553,
  "updated": 1775830276,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69c723f47ecd1447baa531e5",
      "text": "非文芸的サイコソフィア",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774658553,
      "updated": 1775063500
    },
    {
      "id": "69c75c7e00000000000817a1",
      "text": "[Nrem.icon]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774673021,
      "updated": 1774679903
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7775f0000000000d03cbb",
      "text": "　[サイコソフィア]の説明づけを簡潔で理路整然としたモデルに落とし込みたいと思う",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774679903,
      "updated": 1775063027
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7778a0000000000d03cbd",
      "text": "　文学的な説明づけはいらんから構造の全体像を把握させてほしいものです",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774679946,
      "updated": 1774680298
    },
    {
      "id": "69c777610000000000d03cbc",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774679904,
      "updated": 1774679904
    },
    {
      "id": "69c723f90000000000372e67",
      "text": "励起—抑制モデル",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774658553,
      "updated": 1774679904
    },
    {
      "id": "69c724160000000000372e6a",
      "text": "table:仮説（古い版）",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774658582,
      "updated": 1775063531
    },
    {
      "id": "69c724700000000000372e6c",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t1\t\t2\t\t3\t\t4\t",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774658719,
      "updated": 1774698677
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7242c0000000000372e6b",
      "text": "\t\t\t\tP1p\t r1r\tp2p\tR2R\tp3P\tr3R\tP4P\tR4r",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774658719,
      "updated": 1774698675
    },
    {
      "id": "69c724fe0000000000372e70",
      "text": "\t1\tP1p\tr1r\t1\t1\t<\t0\t0\t>\t+\t>",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774658813,
      "updated": 1774698684
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7250e0000000000372e72",
      "text": "\t2\tp2p\tR2R\t>\t0\t1\t1\t-\t>\t0\t-",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774658829,
      "updated": 1774698700
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7254d0000000000372e73",
      "text": "\t3\tp3P\tr3R\t0\t<\t+\t<\t1\t1\t<\t0",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774658892,
      "updated": 1774698714
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7255d0000000000372e74",
      "text": "\t4\tP4P\tR4r\t+\t<\t0\t+\t>\t0\t1\t1",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774658909,
      "updated": 1774698725
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7c1130000000000eb31c9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774698770,
      "updated": 1774698770
    },
    {
      "id": "69c75f7f0000000000d03c1f",
      "text": "フィルターの番号に対応するだろう価値側面（古典的サイコソフィア）",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774673790,
      "updated": 1774685629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c75f290000000000d03c1a",
      "text": "　F – 物質",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774673705,
      "updated": 1774699190
    },
    {
      "id": "69c75f470000000000d03c1e",
      "text": "　L – 知識、論理",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774673734,
      "updated": 1774699188
    },
    {
      "id": "69c75f420000000000d03c1c",
      "text": "　E – 感情、予感",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774673730,
      "updated": 1774673788
    },
    {
      "id": "69c75f440000000000d03c1d",
      "text": "　V – 目的、意志",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774673732,
      "updated": 1774699178
    },
    {
      "id": "69c78d440000000000e892a1",
      "text": "　table: ",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774685507,
      "updated": 1774685549
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7c0ec0000000000eb31c8",
      "text": "　 配列\t\t\t\t\t古典的\t\t\t",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774698732,
      "updated": 1774699635
    },
    {
      "id": "69c78d6d0000000000e892a8",
      "text": "　　1.\t上位\t無意識的\t結果\t過剰\tI+ you-\t\t\t信頼",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774685549,
      "updated": 1774699619
    },
    {
      "id": "69c78d700000000000e892a9",
      "text": "　　2.\t上位\t意識的\t手続き\t\tI+ you+\t川\t柔軟\t信頼",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774685551,
      "updated": 1774699617
    },
    {
      "id": "69c78d720000000000e892aa",
      "text": "　　3.\t下位\t意識的\t手続き\t\tI- you-\t潰瘍\t柔軟\t疑念",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774685554,
      "updated": 1774699611
    },
    {
      "id": "69c78d750000000000e892ab",
      "text": "　　4.\t下位\t無意識的\t結果\t稀少\tI- you+\t依存\t\t信頼できない",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774685556,
      "updated": 1774699615
    },
    {
      "id": "69c75f2a0000000000d03c1b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774673705,
      "updated": 1774673705
    },
    {
      "id": "69c75d4c00000000000817a6",
      "text": "P",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774673228,
      "updated": 1774673231
    },
    {
      "id": "69c75d5100000000000817a7",
      "text": " 便宜的に「手続きフィルター」と呼称する",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774673232,
      "updated": 1774674696
    },
    {
      "id": "69c762fc0000000000d03c36",
      "text": " 今のところ、何の閾値なのかを私自身[Nrem.icon]でも分かっていない",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774674683,
      "updated": 1774685675
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7791a0000000000d03cc5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774680346,
      "updated": 1774680347
    },
    {
      "id": "69c75d4b00000000000817a5",
      "text": "R",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774673226,
      "updated": 1774673261
    },
    {
      "id": "69c76ca90000000000d03c69",
      "text": "　便宜的に「結果フィルター」と呼称する",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774677161,
      "updated": 1774677161
    },
    {
      "id": "69c75d6300000000000817a9",
      "text": "　今のところ、何の閾値なのかを私自身[Nrem.icon]でも分かっていない",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774673251,
      "updated": 1774685680
    },
    {
      "id": "69c75feb0000000000d03c20",
      "text": "　　古典的な[説明づけ]との整合性のために導入してある",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774673899,
      "updated": 1774679242
    },
    {
      "id": "69c773120000000000d03c9b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774678802,
      "updated": 1774678803
    },
    {
      "id": "69c72908000000000094074e",
      "text": "P/p,  R/r",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774659848,
      "updated": 1774659905
    },
    {
      "id": "69c729190000000000940750",
      "text": "　文字の高さは手続きフィルターと結果フィルターの活性化チャネルと抑制チャネルの閾値の高低を表す",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774659865,
      "updated": 1774685690
    },
    {
      "id": "69c762900000000000d03c34",
      "text": "　　本当は上付き文字・下付き文字で表したいところ[Nrem.icon]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774674576,
      "updated": 1774685696
    },
    {
      "id": "69c762bd0000000000d03c35",
      "text": "　　　入力の手間のため、ここでは大文字と小文字で表す",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774674621,
      "updated": 1774683586
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7731e0000000000d03c9c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774678814,
      "updated": 1774678815
    },
    {
      "id": "69c761650000000000d03c29",
      "text": "チャネルの閾値",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774674277,
      "updated": 1774683890
    },
    {
      "id": "69c786f20000000000e89271",
      "text": "　閾値の一致",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774683890,
      "updated": 1774683895
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7616f0000000000d03c2a",
      "text": " 　ある程度の融通が利き、「バランスが取れている」とみなせる",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774674286,
      "updated": 1774683933
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7c3d90000000000eb31dc",
      "text": "　　活動の程度を自己選択できる",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774699481,
      "updated": 1774699483
    },
    {
      "id": "69c786140000000000e89269",
      "text": "  r1r, p2p",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774683706,
      "updated": 1774683910
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7862a0000000000e8926b",
      "text": " 　　弱い信号に反応する",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774683706,
      "updated": 1774683910
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7865d0000000000e8926e",
      "text": " 　　大きな信号に反応しない",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774683741,
      "updated": 1774683910
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7864b0000000000e8926d",
      "text": "  R2R",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774683723,
      "updated": 1774683910
    },
    {
      "id": "69c787310000000000e89272",
      "text": "  　弱い信号に反応しない",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774683953,
      "updated": 1774683957
    },
    {
      "id": "69c787370000000000e89273",
      "text": "  　大きな信号に反応する",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774683958,
      "updated": 1774683986
    },
    {
      "id": "69c775f80000000000d03cb2",
      "text": " 閾値の不一致",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774679543,
      "updated": 1774683923
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7c3870000000000eb31d3",
      "text": " 　活性化チャネルと抑制チャネルのバランスが取れていない",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774699399,
      "updated": 1774699470
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7c3b20000000000eb31d4",
      "text": " 　硬直的",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774699459,
      "updated": 1774699459
    },
    {
      "id": "69c776000000000000d03cb3",
      "text": " 　p3P/r3R",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774679552,
      "updated": 1774683910
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7763e0000000000d03cb4",
      "text": " 　　小さな信号によって頻繁に活性化される",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774679613,
      "updated": 1774684003
    },
    {
      "id": "69c776420000000000d03cb5",
      "text": " 　　大きな信号によってノックダウンされる",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774679618,
      "updated": 1774683910
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7765e0000000000d03cb6",
      "text": " 　P1p, R4r",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774679646,
      "updated": 1774683910
    },
    {
      "id": "69c776700000000000d03cb7",
      "text": " 　　大きな信号にのみ反応する",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774679664,
      "updated": 1774683910
    },
    {
      "id": "69c785fa0000000000e89268",
      "text": " 　　　活性化頻度が低い",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774683706,
      "updated": 1774699399
    },
    {
      "id": "69c785e40000000000e89264",
      "text": " 　　小さな信号によって動作を停止する",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774683698,
      "updated": 1774683910
    },
    {
      "id": "69c777230000000000d03cba",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774679842,
      "updated": 1774679845
    },
    {
      "id": "69c762090000000000d03c30",
      "text": "活性化チャネル",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774674440,
      "updated": 1774674445
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7bfec0000000000eb31c4",
      "text": "　配列の左隣の P/p, R/r のこと",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774698476,
      "updated": 1774698549
    },
    {
      "id": "69c76d1c0000000000d03c74",
      "text": " 活性化チャネルの閾値が低い",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774677276,
      "updated": 1774679166
    },
    {
      "id": "69c76d230000000000d03c79",
      "text": "　　弱い刺激に反応する",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774677283,
      "updated": 1774677284
    },
    {
      "id": "69c774860000000000d03caa",
      "text": "　　大きな信号を無視する",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774679173,
      "updated": 1774679185
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7c4a30000000000eb31e7",
      "text": "　　（弱い信号が強い信号よりも頻繁に発生するという仮定において）活性化頻度が高い",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774699682,
      "updated": 1774699689
    },
    {
      "id": "69c772390000000000d03c99",
      "text": "　活性化チャネルの閾値が高い",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774678584,
      "updated": 1774678836
    },
    {
      "id": "69c781190000000000e8925d",
      "text": "　　大きな信号によって励起される",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774682392,
      "updated": 1774682392
    },
    {
      "id": "69c774940000000000d03cab",
      "text": "　　弱い刺激を無視する",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774679188,
      "updated": 1774679195
    },
    {
      "id": "69c773260000000000d03c9f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774678822,
      "updated": 1774678822
    },
    {
      "id": "69c762350000000000d03c32",
      "text": "抑制チャネル",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774674485,
      "updated": 1774677293
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7c00f0000000000eb31c5",
      "text": "　配列の右隣の P/p, R/r のこと",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774698511,
      "updated": 1774698553
    },
    {
      "id": "69c761b10000000000d03c2d",
      "text": "　抑制チャネルの閾値が低い",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774674352,
      "updated": 1774677294
    },
    {
      "id": "69c761c80000000000d03c2e",
      "text": "　　大きな信号を無視する、または励起される",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774674375,
      "updated": 1774682422
    },
    {
      "id": "69c76d390000000000d03c7a",
      "text": "　　フィードバックの信号が小さい場合にフィルターが停止する",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774677304,
      "updated": 1774678596
    },
    {
      "id": "69c76ce40000000000d03c6b",
      "text": "　抑制チャネルの閾値が高い",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774677219,
      "updated": 1774677295
    },
    {
      "id": "69c76cee0000000000d03c6c",
      "text": "　　大きな信号によってノックダウンされる",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774677229,
      "updated": 1774677298
    },
    {
      "id": "69c775650000000000d03caf",
      "text": "　　小さい信号に反応しない",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774679397,
      "updated": 1774679428
    },
    {
      "id": "69c76cf30000000000d03c6d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774677235,
      "updated": 1774677235
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7733c0000000000d03ca1",
      "text": "[** 記号類]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774678844,
      "updated": 1774699709
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7347e0000000000889d90",
      "text": "同属`1`",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774662782,
      "updated": 1774683479
    },
    {
      "id": "69c734880000000000889d91",
      "text": "　二者のフィルターの間で活性化チャネルと抑制チャネルの閾値が一致する",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774662791,
      "updated": 1774662872
    },
    {
      "id": "69c734b00000000000889d92",
      "text": "　相互理解が早い",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774662831,
      "updated": 1774662928
    },
    {
      "id": "69c734f70000000000889d93",
      "text": "　[_ 互いの目標が一致する限り]、円滑に共同作業を行うことができる",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774662903,
      "updated": 1774673140
    },
    {
      "id": "69c735460000000000889d94",
      "text": "　誤りの訂正が行われない",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774662982,
      "updated": 1774663036
    },
    {
      "id": "69c735a60000000000889d97",
      "text": "　同じところで躓く",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774663077,
      "updated": 1774663101
    },
    {
      "id": "69c75cfd00000000000817a2",
      "text": "無視`0`",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774673149,
      "updated": 1774673164
    },
    {
      "id": "69c75d1c00000000000817a4",
      "text": "　二者のフィルターの間で活性化チャネルと抑制チャネルの閾値がそれぞれ異なっている",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774673180,
      "updated": 1774674085
    },
    {
      "id": "69c760b90000000000d03c24",
      "text": "　素通りする",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774674104,
      "updated": 1774674115
    },
    {
      "id": "69c760790000000000d03c23",
      "text": "　　関心のあり方が異なることにより会話が発生しない",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774674041,
      "updated": 1774674106
    },
    {
      "id": "69c75dc500000000000817ab",
      "text": "　　無関心、またはもどかしさが生じる",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774673349,
      "updated": 1774679486
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7c04e0000000000eb31c6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774698574,
      "updated": 1774698575
    },
    {
      "id": "69c727930000000000940741",
      "text": "誘発`-`",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774659475,
      "updated": 1774662145
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7280f0000000000940744",
      "text": "　活性化チャネルと抑制チャネルの閾値が他方の活性化チャネルと一致する",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774659599,
      "updated": 1774662077
    },
    {
      "id": "69c731df0000000000889d80",
      "text": "　励起状態を誘発する",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774662111,
      "updated": 1774662136
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7610f0000000000d03c28",
      "text": "　一方向のエネルギーの受け渡しが生じる",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774674192,
      "updated": 1774674205
    },
    {
      "id": "69c760e90000000000d03c27",
      "text": "　ソシオニクスの用語でいうところの「恩恵関係」に類似する",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774674153,
      "updated": 1774674184
    },
    {
      "id": "69c727a80000000000940742",
      "text": "被誘発`+`",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774659495,
      "updated": 1774678857
    },
    {
      "id": "69c728150000000000940745",
      "text": "　活性化チャネルと抑制チャネルの信号が一致せず、他方から活性化チャネルの信号のみ受け取る状態",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774659605,
      "updated": 1774674255
    },
    {
      "id": "69c760e30000000000d03c26",
      "text": "　励起される側",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774674147,
      "updated": 1774674151
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7c0570000000000eb31c7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774698582,
      "updated": 1774698583
    },
    {
      "id": "69c728480000000000940748",
      "text": "制御`>`",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774659656,
      "updated": 1774678860
    },
    {
      "id": "69c728400000000000940746",
      "text": "　活性化チャネルと抑制チャネルの閾値が一致しており、その閾値が他方の抑制チャネルと一致する",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774659648,
      "updated": 1774660934
    },
    {
      "id": "69c72897000000000094074a",
      "text": "被制御`<`",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774659734,
      "updated": 1774678862
    },
    {
      "id": "69c728a8000000000094074c",
      "text": "　活性化チャネルと抑制チャネルの閾値が一致しておらず、抑制チャネルが他方の活性化―抑制チャネルと一致する",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774659752,
      "updated": 1774659823
    },
    {
      "id": "69c760cf0000000000d03c25",
      "text": "　不満が生じる",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774674126,
      "updated": 1774674131
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7289f000000000094074b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774659743,
      "updated": 1774659743
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7783f0000000000d03cbf",
      "text": "[hr.icon]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774680126,
      "updated": 1774680489
    },
    {
      "id": "69c778400000000000d03cc0",
      "text": "[非文芸的サイコソフィア: 二者間の反応モデル]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774680128,
      "updated": 1775830276
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7bf870000000000eb31c1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774698375,
      "updated": 1774698375
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7bf870000000000eb31c2",
      "text": "#怪文書の書き方",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1774698375,
      "updated": 1774698383
    }
  ]
}